com.barryholroyd.evermore.debugging.controlpanel.spinners

Class SpinnerMockloc

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.barryholroyd.evermore.debugging.controlpanel.spinners.SpinnerMockloc

  • public class SpinnerMockloc
extends java.lang.Object
    Convenience class for defining methods called from the control panel. Called from ControlPanelSpinner.runMethod() via Java reflection. *** THIS IS ONLY VALID FOR THE LIST SCREEN. IT DOES NOT AFFECT *** THE DEVICE'S UNDERSTANDING OF LOCATION (e.g., the map on the *** Main and Map screens will be unaffected). This is only *** provided for basic testing of location and bearing combinations. topView is the top of the Control Panel Dialog Fragment view hierarchy. Note that spinner0 gets run by the system automatically when the Spinner is (re-)created.
